        "html": "<!-- header 2 -->\r\n<h2>10.1 - About Page</h2>\r\n\r\n<!-- paragraph -->\r\n<p>\r\n    The About Page provides an overview of the system, including its version details, developers involved, and contact information for support.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<!-- centered image -->\r\n<center><img src=\"images/user-manual/about.png\"></img></center>\r\n<!-- centered and italic -->\r\n<center><i>The about screen</i></center>\r\n\r\n<!-- Ordered List (1., 2., ...)-->\r\n<ol>\r\n\t<!-- list item -->\r\n\t<li>\r\n\t\t<b>System Overview</b> - This section offers a brief explanation of the system's functionality and purpose, highlighting its main features and benefits for the users.\r\n\t</li>\r\n    <li>\r\n\t\t<b>Version</b> - This section provides the version number of the system, detailing the current release and any notable updates or changes included in this version.\r\n\t</li>\r\n    <li>\r\n\t\t<b>Developers</b> - This section provides information about the development team including their roles and essential contact details for support, allowing users to know where to seek help if needed.\r\n\t</li>\r\n</ol>"
